## Notes / history

We previously observed a case where inserts appeared to succeed via JDBC but did not show up in Access / file timestamp.
After updating and pinning dependency versions (UCanAccess + Jackcess + HSQLDB), and tuning the connection URL,
pooling writes were verified to persist using `/health/dbSignature`.

Keep this file updated when we add new DB health endpoints.
